snippet.title: Those Who Rule  - Official Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Gameplay Showcase Trailer for Tactical RPG - Those Who Rule

Jump into the world with our free 4-chapter demo! Command a squad of fresh recruits, master turn-based combat, and make tough choices that shape a war-torn world. We’d love to hear your thoughts!

Feedback form: bit.ly/3YgDUMC

Song - The Epic Odyssey Rock Fantasy - Yurii Panivan

Follow updates and wishlist on Steam and Twitter!

https://store.steampowered.com/app/1822060/Those_Who_Rule/
https://twitter.com/ThoseWhoRule
